### Mocking Strategy

- **API Mocks**: Use jest.spyOn for formService methods in unit/integration tests
- **Component Mocks**: Mock child components when testing parent components
- **Hook Mocks**: Mock custom hooks when testing components that use them
- **Timer Mocks**: Use jest.useFakeTimers() for timeout testing
